sql:
SELECT p.product_name, s.shipment_date
FROM Products p
JOIN Order_Items oi ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
JOIN Shipment_Items si ON oi.order_item_id = si.order_item_id
JOIN Shipments s ON si.shipment_id = s.shipment_id;
question: What are the names of the products tht have been shipped, and on what days were they shipped?

SELECT Products.product_name, Shipments.shipment_date
FROM Shipments

JOIN Order_Items ON Shipment_Items.order_item_id = Order_Items.order_item_id
JOIN Products ON Order_Items.product_id = Products.product_id;
